        <mxCell id="e6" edge="1" parent="1" source="dragonfly" style="endArrow=classic;html=1;rounded=0;dashed=1;exitX=1;exitY=0;exitDx=0;exitDy=0;entryX=0;entryY=1;entryDx=0;entryDy=0;" target="redisinsight" value="browse">
          <mxGeometry height="50" relative="1" width="50" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="requirements-note" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff9e6;strokeColor=#d6b656;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=8;spacingTop=6;fontSize=10;fontColor=#0B0B0B;" value="&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(11, 11, 11);&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(11, 11, 11);&quot;&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(11, 11, 11);&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(11, 11, 11);&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(11, 11, 11);&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(11, 11, 11);&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;• Trade schema: symbol, price, quantity, timestamp (ISO8601), trade_id — Producer + Bridge store full JSON.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(11, 11, 11);&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;• Ingestion: ~50k eps, spikes to 500k; no backpressure to Kafka — Pull-based consumer; scale bridge + partitions for production.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(11, 11, 11);&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;• Symbol scale: 12k symbols, 500–1k hot — One LIST per symbol (trades:SYMBOL); scales to 12k+ keys.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(11, 11, 11);&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;• Retention: last 10 trades per symbol only — LPUSH + LTRIM 0 9 (see Bridge → Dragonfly).&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(11, 11, 11);&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;• Frontend query: REST API → data store; &amp;lt;1 ms from store — Query API uses LRANGE 0 9; benchmark shows sub-ms latency.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(11, 11, 11);&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;• Client: Redis-compatible; &amp;lt;1 ms target — Use official Redis client (redis-py, ioredis, go-redis, Jedis, etc.); Dragonfly-compatible.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="250" width="940" x="40" y="600" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="stakeholder-note" parent="1" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=10;fontStyle=3;fontColor=#666666;" value="&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(11, 11, 11); font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;Stakeholder ask: Simple, reproducible bridge into Dragonfly so frontend can query live data in sub-milliseconds&lt;/font&gt;" vertex="1">
